Class Translation

java.lang.Object
com.erudika.para.core.Translation
All Implemented Interfaces:
Linkable, ParaObject, Votable, Serializable
public class Translation extends Object implements ParaObject
A translation is a key/value pair which holds a single translated string. For example: hello = "Hola"
Author:
Alex Bogdanovski [alex@erudika.com]
